{"tid":1441451,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[會員牙笠入一入黎]MOMOLAND再傳兩成員「退團」？經紀公司至今沒回應...讓粉絲心碎！","createTime":"2019-08-10T16:08:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T16:18:54.000Z","uid":238483,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b2d35b0cd03f42d4b3f7f66086327ca04f36ec2e","tid":1441451,"uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:08:29.000Z","msg":"粉絲一定相當難過啊...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3003080/org/9662527aa2116a9445907f36b90dc678.jpg/TQiithfLAb6gwrrxX1ym4K3pUq4CAJobRltn7EZbZ-w?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3003080%2Forg%2F9662527aa2116a9445907f36b90dc678.jpg%2FTQiithfLAb6gwrrxX1ym4K3pUq4CAJobRltn7EZbZ-w%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=3e6b47b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n說到三大公司除外，發展不錯的女團，想必不少粉絲會想到MOMOLAND吧！但前一陣子有妍雨「退團傳聞」，讓粉絲相當驚慌，還好後來經紀公司澄清謠言，妍雨本人在官方論壇發表文字聲明，才讓粉絲鬆了一口氣。<br />\n<br />\n但最近又傳出成員的退團消息，讓粉絲相當錯愕。MOMOLAND是九人女團，但從三月開始，就以少了泰河和DAISY的形式進行七人組活動。<br />\n<br />\n加上官方IG成員們也沒有提及泰河和DAISY，最決定性的原因就是MOMOLAND出道一千日，<span style=\"color: red;\">公開了成員手寫信等等感謝的訊息，但卻不是完全體，而是只有七位成員。</span><br />\n<br />\n值得紀念的日子，粉絲卻等不到泰河和DAISY的手寫信，讓粉絲相當失望！<br />\n如今六個月都沒有泰河和DAISY的消息，讓粉絲擔心起兩人是否即將退團，也向經紀公司提出質問。<br />\n但也有可能是成員的健康問題或個人因素，只希望經紀公司儘快出面說明啊！給粉絲一點交代～<br />\n<br />\n你個笠水狗仲要燈死幾多隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下開放不推文回覆"},{"pid":"204b68533345c263da365639da6517340da429b5","tid":1441451,"uid":46435,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:11:38.000Z","msg":"係退都退個隊長同埋另一個叫唔出名果個啦.."},{"pid":"648fba1543eafdeca82b29ce0bcf1a8c6c43e34a","tid":1441451,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:12:46.000Z","msg":"NANCY 妍雨退團好過啦"},{"pid":"406fc0f80299c2c6e6a6d9f85c86a3687a091f9c","tid":1441451,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:14:14.000Z","msg":"nancy仲未肥完。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早知平時帶套 唔逼佢長期食藥。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef2f14f42f12889abce359d4c790084a4a65cb5","tid":1441451,"uid":193951,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"648fba1543eafdeca82b29ce0bcf1a8c6c43e34a","tid":1441451,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:12:46.000Z","msg":"NANCY 妍雨退團好過啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:18:54.000Z","msg":"妍雨退團同我給婚"}]}